				At the KC entrance I can still blind Drolvarg Ragers with this spell. Root, DoT, Snare, Sunbeam, DD and just stay outta range in the Foyer; get an add? np Root the add, Snare, Sunbeam when Root breaks, DoT, DD, Sunbeam, kill the 1st Rager and /em snarl %t 2nd Rager. You can sit and med back a bubb whilst keeping an eye on your 2nd Rager, he's snared but he'll still try and rush you anyway. Put him out of his misery.
