				You all obviously are missing this spells great use. As a druid at level 24 you also get the spell Pogonip which is a AE 180ish DD with snare effect. With a vary tinked out wis of 200 a level 24 druid has 1008 mana. 125 mana for pog and 40 for sunbeam you can roughly smack down a group of mobs for ~1000dmg. This is the start of the technique called quad-kiting. Start off with the pogonip for the aggro and snare. They should group up together closely while they are comming after you. Run a bit and turn and cast sunbeam for the AE &quot;mez&quot; like effect when needed for medding otherwise just continue to q-kite with pogonip. Super mana efficient way to get phat amounts of exp all in one show, hella fun too and when a foo comes up and trys to take your camp.. tell em you ownz.<BR>
<BR>
Strahm Grymblade 48 war<BR>
Faylee Windtear 24 dru<BR>
Nailosi 16 nec<BR>
Jadeaia 12 enc
				</font>
			</td>

