				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Merry Meet,<BR>
<BR>
   This spell is though of as an attack spell.  Just like any attack spell, it can be cast on any NPC and yourself.  No other PC will be harmed by any attack spell (unless, like posted above, you are on a PvP server).  <BR>
   Heck, if you want to test this, don't ask someone to stand by a NPC while you cast, just cast it straight on the PC.  Won't do anything to him,  Unless PvP.<BR>
   &lt;SideNote&gt; on the previous post the person stated after battle to Gate, Sow, Soc, whatever.  I would hope no druid would have to cast SoW for an escape as, any druid should know you never let SoW down, and at the level of this spell, you should never let WolfForm down when fighting.<BR>
<BR>
Merry Part,<BR>
